---
import ServiceLayout from '../../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title="Financial reporting for Ontario businesses | Barrana Accounting Services"
  description="Monthly financial reporting support for Ontario businesses, including recurring reporting packages and CPA-reviewed visibility."
  serviceTitle="Financial reporting"
  tagline="Reporting that gives you better visibility into your business"
  deliveryApproach="We support reporting through cleaner bookkeeping, recurring reporting workflows, and CPA review where needed. The goal is to help business owners receive more consistent visibility into their numbers without having to request it each time."
  whatClientsGain="More regular financial visibility. Reports that arrive on a consistent schedule rather than on request. Better context for decisions about cash flow, expenses, and business direction."
  includes={[
    'Recurring monthly financial reporting package',
    'Profit and loss statement',
    'Balance sheet',
    'Cash flow statement',
    'Period-over-period comparison where appropriate',
    'CPA commentary on significant items',
    'Coordination with underlying bookkeeping and filing work',
    'Annual financial statements where needed',
  ]}
  forWho="Ontario businesses that want more regular visibility into performance and do not want reporting to be an afterthought that only surfaces at year-end."
  pricingNote="Included in selected ongoing plans depending on reporting frequency and complexity."
>
  <Fragment slot="what-this-is">
    <p>Financial reporting helps you understand how the business is performing, what is changing, and where attention may be needed. That usually means recurring profit and loss reporting, balance sheet visibility, cash flow context, and commentary where appropriate.</p>
    <p>Reports are only useful when they are based on current records and delivered in a way the business can actually use.</p>
  </Fragment>
</ServiceLayout>
